Note:
Runa Advanced Standard Library: Macro Code Generation Module

Provides advanced code generation capabilities for macros including:
- Template-based code generation
- AST-based code synthesis
- Dynamic code construction
- Code optimization and transformation
- Cross-language code generation
- Code validation and verification
- AI/agent-friendly code generation tools
- Production-ready code generation with error handling

Features:
- Advanced template-based code generation with variable substitution
- AST-based code synthesis with structural manipulation
- Dynamic code construction with runtime generation
- Code optimization and transformation with performance tuning
- Cross-language code generation with language-specific backends
- Comprehensive code validation and verification
- AI/agent-friendly code generation development tools
- Production-ready code generation with comprehensive error handling
:End Note

Note: Code Generation Types and Data Structures
Type CodeGenerator is Dictionary with:
    context as MacroContext
    template_engine as TemplateEngine
    ast_generator as ASTGenerator
    code_synthesizer as CodeSynthesizer
    optimizer as CodeOptimizer
    validator as CodeValidator
    debug_tracer as CodeGenerationDebugTracer
    performance_monitor as CodeGenerationPerformanceMonitor
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type TemplateEngine is Dictionary with:
    templates as Dictionary[String, CodeTemplate]
    processors as Dictionary[String, TemplateProcessorFunction]
    renderers as Dictionary[String, TemplateRendererFunction]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ASTGenerator is Dictionary with:
    generators as Dictionary[String, ASTGeneratorFunction]
    transformers as Dictionary[String, ASTTransformerFunction]
    builders as Dictionary[String, ASTBuilderFunction]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeSynthesizer is Dictionary with:
    synthesizers as Dictionary[String, CodeSynthesizerFunction]
    analyzers as Dictionary[String, CodeAnalyzerFunction]
    generators as Dictionary[String, CodeGeneratorFunction]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeOptimizer is Dictionary with:
    optimizers as Dictionary[String, CodeOptimizerFunction]
    analyzers as Dictionary[String, CodeOptimizationAnalyzerFunction]
    transformers as Dictionary[String, CodeOptimizationTransformerFunction]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeValidator is Dictionary with:
    validators as Dictionary[String, CodeValidatorFunction]
    checkers as Dictionary[String, CodeCheckerFunction]
    verifiers as Dictionary[String, CodeVerifierFunction]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationDebugTracer is Dictionary with:
    trace_level as String
    trace_output as List[CodeGenerationTraceEntry]
    generation_events as List[CodeGenerationEvent]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationPerformanceMonitor is Dictionary with:
    metrics as Dictionary[String, CodeGenerationPerformanceMetric]
    thresholds as Dictionary[String, Float]
    alerts as List[CodeGenerationPerformanceAlert]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeTemplate is Dictionary with:
    template_id as String
    template_type as String
    template_code as String
    variables as List[TemplateVariable]
    sections as List[TemplateSection]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type TemplateVariable is Dictionary with:
    name as String
    variable_type as String
    default_value as Any
    validation_rules as List[ValidationRule]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type TemplateSection is Dictionary with:
    section_id as String
    section_type as String
    content as String
    conditions as List[String]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type TemplateProcessorFunction is Function that takes template as CodeTemplate and variables as Dictionary[String, Any] returns ProcessedTemplate

Type TemplateRendererFunction is Function that takes processed_template as ProcessedTemplate and context as Dictionary[String, Any] returns String

Type ASTGeneratorFunction is Function that takes ast_spec as ASTSpecification and context as Dictionary[String, Any] returns ASTNode

Type ASTTransformerFunction is Function that takes ast_node as ASTNode and transformation as ASTTransformation returns ASTNode

Type ASTBuilderFunction is Function that takes builder_spec as ASTBuilderSpecification returns ASTNode

Type CodeSynthesizerFunction is Function that takes synthesis_spec as CodeSynthesisSpecification returns GeneratedCode

Type CodeAnalyzerFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode returns CodeAnalysis

Type CodeGeneratorFunction is Function that takes generation_spec as CodeGenerationSpecification returns GeneratedCode

Type CodeOptimizerFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode returns OptimizedCode

Type CodeOptimizationAnalyzerFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode returns OptimizationAnalysis

Type CodeOptimizationTransformerFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode and optimization as OptimizationSpecification returns OptimizedCode

Type CodeValidatorFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode returns ValidationResult

Type CodeCheckerFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode returns CheckResult

Type CodeVerifierFunction is Function that takes code as GeneratedCode returns VerificationResult

Type ProcessedTemplate is Dictionary with:
    template_id as String
    processed_content as String
    variable_bindings as Dictionary[String, Any]
    sections as List[ProcessedSection]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ProcessedSection is Dictionary with:
    section_id as String
    processed_content as String
    is_active as Boolean
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ASTSpecification is Dictionary with:
    node_type as String
    properties as Dictionary[String, Any]
    children as List[ASTSpecification]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ASTTransformation is Dictionary with:
    transformation_type as String
    parameters as Dictionary[String, Any]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ASTBuilderSpecification is Dictionary with:
    builder_type as String
    configuration as Dictionary[String, Any]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeSynthesisSpecification is Dictionary with:
    synthesis_type as String
    template as CodeTemplate
    variables as Dictionary[String, Any]
    options as Dictionary[String, Any]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type GeneratedCode is Dictionary with:
    code_type as String
    content as String
    ast as ASTNode
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]
    performance_metrics as Dictionary[String, Float]

Type CodeAnalysis is Dictionary with:
    complexity as Float
    size as Integer
    quality_score as Float
    issues as List[CodeIssue]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationSpecification is Dictionary with:
    generation_type as String
    target_language as String
    ast_specification as ASTSpecification
    options as Dictionary[String, Any]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type OptimizedCode is Dictionary with:
    original_code as GeneratedCode
    optimized_content as String
    optimizations_applied as List[String]
    performance_improvement as Float
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type OptimizationAnalysis is Dictionary with:
    optimization_opportunities as List[String]
    estimated_improvement as Float
    complexity_impact as Float
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type OptimizationSpecification is Dictionary with:
    optimization_type as String
    parameters as Dictionary[String, Any]
    constraints as List[String]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ValidationResult is:
    | ValidationSuccess with code as GeneratedCode and score as Float and metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]
    | ValidationError with error as String and details as Dictionary[String, Any]
    | ValidationWarning with warning as String and code as GeneratedCode and metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CheckResult is Dictionary with:
    passed as Boolean
    issues as List[CodeIssue]
    score as Float
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type VerificationResult is Dictionary with:
    verified as Boolean
    proof as String
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeIssue is Dictionary with:
    issue_type as String
    severity as String
    message as String
    location as CodeLocation
    suggestions as List[String]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeLocation is Dictionary with:
    line as Integer
    column as Integer
    offset as Integer
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationTraceEntry is Dictionary with:
    timestamp as Float
    level as String
    message as String
    template_id as String
    action as String
    data as Dictionary[String, Any]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationEvent is Dictionary with:
    event_type as String
    timestamp as Float
    template_id as String
    details as Dictionary[String, Any]
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationPerformanceMetric is Dictionary with:
    name as String
    value as Float
    unit as String
    timestamp as Float
    template_id as String
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type CodeGenerationPerformanceAlert is Dictionary with:
    metric as String
    threshold as Float
    current_value as Float
    severity as String
    timestamp as Float
    template_id as String
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Note: Core Code Generation Functions
Process called "create_code_generator" that takes context as MacroContext returns CodeGenerator:
    Let template_engine be create_template_engine with context as context
    Let ast_generator be create_ast_generator with context as context
    Let code_synthesizer be create_code_synthesizer with context as context
    Let optimizer be create_code_optimizer with context as context
    Let validator be create_code_validator with context as context
    Let debug_tracer be create_code_generation_debug_tracer with context as context
    Let performance_monitor be create_code_generation_performance_monitor with context as context
    
    Return CodeGenerator with:
        context as context
        template_engine as template_engine
        ast_generator as ast_generator
        code_synthesizer as code_synthesizer
        optimizer as optimizer
        validator as validator
        debug_tracer as debug_tracer
        performance_monitor as performance_monitor
        metadata as dictionary containing

Process called "generate_code_from_template" that takes generator as CodeGenerator and template_id as String and variables as Dictionary[String, Any] returns GeneratedCode:
    Let start_time be get_current_time
    
    Try:
        Let trace_entry be CodeGenerationTraceEntry with:
            timestamp as start_time
            level as "info"
            message as "Starting code generation from template: " plus template_id
            template_id as template_id
            action as "start_generation"
            data as dictionary containing:
                "variable_count" as length of variables
            metadata as dictionary containing
        
        Add trace_entry to generator.debug_tracer.trace_output
        
        Let template be generator.template_engine.templates[template_id] if generator.template_engine.templates contains template_id else None
        
        If template is None:
            Return GeneratedCode with:
                code_type as "error"
                content as "Template not found: " plus template_id
                ast as create_error_ast with message as "Template not found"
                metadata as dictionary containing
                performance_metrics as dictionary containing
        
        Let processed_template be process_template with generator as generator and template as template and variables as variables
        
        Let rendered_code be render_template with generator as generator and processed_template as processed_template and context as dictionary containing
        
        Let generated_ast be generate_ast_from_code with generator as generator and code as rendered_code
        
        Let generated_code be GeneratedCode with:
            code_type as template.template_type
            content as rendered_code
            ast as generated_ast
            metadata as dictionary containing:
                "template_id" as template_id
                "variable_count" as length of variables
            performance_metrics as dictionary containing:
                "generation_time" as get_current_time minus start_time
        
        Let optimized_code be optimize_generated_code with generator as generator and code as generated_code
        
        Let validation_result be validate_generated_code with generator as generator and code as optimized_code
        
        Let end_time be get_current_time
        Let final_trace_entry be CodeGenerationTraceEntry with:
            timestamp as end_time
            level as "info"
            message as "Completed code generation from template: " plus template_id
            template_id as template_id
            action as "complete_generation"
            data as dictionary containing:
                "code_length" as length of optimized_code.optimized_content
                "generation_time" as end_time minus start_time
            metadata as dictionary containing
        
        Add final_trace_entry to generator.debug_tracer.trace_output
        
        Return optimized_code
        
    Catch error:
        Let error_trace_entry be CodeGenerationTraceEntry with:
            timestamp as get_current_time
            level as "error"
            message as "Code generation failed: " plus error.message
            template_id as template_id
            action as "generation_error"
            data as dictionary containing:
                "error" as error.message
            metadata as dictionary containing
        
        Add error_trace_entry to generator.debug_tracer.trace_output
        
        Return GeneratedCode with:
            code_type as "error"
            content as "Code generation failed: " plus error.message
            ast as create_error_ast with message as error.message
            metadata as dictionary containing
            performance_metrics as dictionary containing

Process called "generate_code_from_ast" that takes generator as CodeGenerator and ast_spec as ASTSpecification and target_language as String returns GeneratedCode:
    Let start_time be get_current_time
    
    Try:
        Let ast_node be generate_ast_from_specification with generator as generator and ast_spec as ast_spec
        
        Let code_generation_spec be CodeGenerationSpecification with:
            generation_type as "ast_to_code"
            target_language as target_language
            ast_specification as ast_spec
            options as dictionary containing
            metadata as dictionary containing
        
        Let generated_code be generate_code_from_specification with generator as generator and spec as code_generation_spec
        
        Let end_time be get_current_time
        Set generated_code.performance_metrics["ast_generation_time"] to end_time minus start_time
        
        Return generated_code
        
    Catch error:
        Return GeneratedCode with:
            code_type as "error"
            content as "AST-based code generation failed: " plus error.message
            ast as create_error_ast with message as error.message
            metadata as dictionary containing
            performance_metrics as dictionary containing

Process called "synthesize_code" that takes generator as CodeGenerator and synthesis_spec as CodeSynthesisSpecification returns GeneratedCode:
    Let start_time be get_current_time
    
    Try:
        Let synthesizer_function be generator.code_synthesizer.synthesizers[synthesis_spec.synthesis_type] if generator.code_synthesizer.synthesizers contains synthesis_spec.synthesis_type else default_code_synthesizer
        
        Let generated_code be synthesizer_function with synthesis_spec as synthesis_spec
        
        Let analysis be analyze_generated_code with generator as generator and code as generated_code
        
        Let end_time be get_current_time
        Set generated_code.performance_metrics["synthesis_time"] to end_time minus start_time
        Set generated_code.metadata["analysis"] to analysis
        
        Return generated_code
        
    Catch error:
        Return GeneratedCode with:
            code_type as "error"
            content as "Code synthesis failed: " plus error.message
            ast as create_error_ast with message as error.message
            metadata as dictionary containing
            performance_metrics as dictionary containing

Note: Template Engine Functions
Process called "create_template_engine" that takes context as MacroContext returns TemplateEngine:
    Let templates be dictionary containing
    Let processors be dictionary containing:
        "simple" as simple_template_processor
        "conditional" as conditional_template_processor
        "loop" as loop_template_processor
        "nested" as nested_template_processor
    
    Let renderers be dictionary containing:
        "text" as text_template_renderer
        "code" as code_template_renderer
        "html" as html_template_renderer
    
    Return TemplateEngine with:
        templates as templates
        processors as processors
        renderers as renderers
        metadata as dictionary containing

Process called "register_template" that takes generator as CodeGenerator and template as CodeTemplate returns Boolean:
    Try:
        Set generator.template_engine.templates[template.template_id] to template
        Return true
        
    Catch error:
        Return false

Process called "process_template" that takes generator as CodeGenerator and template as CodeTemplate and variables as Dictionary[String, Any] returns ProcessedTemplate:
    Try:
        Let processor_function be generator.template_engine.processors[template.template_type] if generator.template_engine.processors contains template.template_type else default_template_processor
        
        Let processed_template be processor_function with template as template and variables as variables
        
        Return processed_template
        
    Catch error:
        Return ProcessedTemplate with:
            template_id as template.template_id
            processed_content as "Template processing failed"
            variable_bindings as variables
            sections as list containing
            metadata as dictionary containing

Process called "render_template" that takes generator as CodeGenerator and processed_template as ProcessedTemplate and context as Dictionary[String, Any] returns String:
    Try:
        Let renderer_function be generator.template_engine.renderers["code"] if generator.template_engine.renderers contains "code" else default_template_renderer
        
        Let rendered_code be renderer_function with processed_template as processed_template and context as context
        
        Return rendered_code
        
    Catch error:
        Return "Template rendering failed: " plus error.message

Process called "simple_template_processor" that takes template as CodeTemplate and variables as Dictionary[String, Any] returns ProcessedTemplate:
    Note: Simple template processor implementation
    Return ProcessedTemplate with:
        template_id as template.template_id
        processed_content as template.template_code
        variable_bindings as variables
        sections as list containing
        metadata as dictionary containing

Process called "conditional_template_processor" that takes template as CodeTemplate and variables as Dictionary[String, Any] returns ProcessedTemplate:
